README
======

legendas.tv - search and download subtitles from legendas.tv site

INSTALL
=======

Add to /etc/apt/sources.list

deb http://sede.colivre.coop.br/~joenio/debian/ ./

And run

# apt-get update
# apt-get install legendas-tv

EXAMPLES
========

$ legendas.tv search -s 'Star Wars'

$ legendas.tv psearch --dir /tmp/folder --file /movies/file.avi

$ legendas.tv logout

